Who is you.

00:36:40.125 --> 00:36:41.125
Ladybug.

00:36:41.326 --> 00:36:42.075
I'm Fei

00:36:42.125 --> 00:36:44.267
You are one of the good guys?

00:36:44.659 --> 00:36:45.232
Yes

00:36:48.953 --> 00:36:52.758
I will finally be able to check if this investment was profitable.

00:36:52.783 --> 00:36:58.814
So you were my mysterious buyer! An uninteresting trinket like that never brought me so much money!

00:36:58.839 --> 00:37:00.318
*Cruel laugh*

00:37:08.537 --> 00:37:11.537
I have been waiting for this moment for 15 long years now.

00:37:15.869 --> 00:37:16.869
Oh it's my bracelet!

00:37:17.026 --> 00:37:18.026
