Nooooooo!

00:38:17.927 --> 00:38:18.927
I take over my father's mission!

00:38:20.513 --> 00:38:21.513
Fei, I told you to stay hidden!

00:38:22.037 --> 00:38:25.358
So it's you who will affront my judgment, Human.

00:38:35.407 --> 00:38:36.407
Hurry up Cat Noir.

