Normally, if I turn into a dragon I can control all the elements.

00:40:54.973 --> 00:40:57.973
I’d really like to toast his armor with lightning, but it’s not working.

00:40:59.059 --> 00:41:02.450
The power of the dragon is the most powerful of them all.

