00:41:06.211 --> 00:41:07.816
Of course my intentions are noble !

00:41:07.841 --> 00:41:09.991
I want revenge from the man who ruined my life.

00:41:10.016 --> 00:41:15.742
Revenge is against the dragon’s values.
Your intentions and your judgement are troubled.

00:41:15.767 --> 00:41:17.767
Isn’t revenge the same thing as justice ?

00:41:18.067 --> 00:41:21.067
So we’ll defeat him another way. Ho !

00:41:37.381 --> 00:41:38.150
No !

00:41:38.175 --> 00:41:43.175
Who would have thought, the prodigious and your miraculous on the same day!

00:41:55.952 --> 00:41:57.952
Cataclysm !

00:42:01.511 --> 00:42:04.511
Nooo !

00:42:05.006 --> 00:42:06.210
Where is my money ?

00:42:08.496 --> 00:42:11.496
You’re alone against 3 of us Hawkmoth. It’s over.

00:42:11.599 --> 00:42:14.599
I think you mean it’s over for you.

00:42:22.091 --> 00:42:24.544
Yan Woshi, I am Hawkmoth.

00:42:24.569 --> 00:42:30.569
You will certainly not let this girl, who gets revenge and justice confused, be the holder of your prodigious.

00:42:30.594 --> 00:42:37.594
As the Yama infernal sovereign, I will sow carnage and destruction until she gives me back the jewel !

00:42:47.927 --> 00:42:50.658
We have to break the ball, the akuma is inside.

00:42:53.745 --> 00:42:55.216
Tremble, humans !

00:42:56.075 --> 00:42:57.169
Ah!

00:42:57.756 --> 00:43:00.851
Adrien! No! Not the City!

00:43:00.876 --> 00:43:03.876
Yan Woshi ! Stop or I’ll take back your power-

00:43:04.641 --> 00:43:07.641
I take orders from no one !

00:43:09.322 --> 00:43:13.322
Okay… Is that good or bad news ?

00:43:17.010 --> 00:43:21.010
We recharge and regroup to think of a plan.

00:43:44.483 --> 00:43:46.483
Ying !

00:43:49.130 --> 00:43:51.130
Roa !

00:43:58.199 --> 00:44:00.251
Hua !

00:44:09.637 --> 00:44:10.969
Everything is my fault.

00:44:10.994 --> 00:44:14.994
Give me the prodigious back. You are not worthy of wearing it.

00:44:15.736 --> 00:44:16.437
He is right.

00:44:16.462 --> 00:44:17.462
No !

00:44:17.818 --> 00:44:19.300
You’re the only one who can defeat him.

00:44:19.325 --> 00:44:23.325
Only the power of the dragon can reach the akumatized object inside of him.

00:44:23.350 --> 00:44:27.350
I want to be able to use the power of the dragon. But I am not worthy of it.

00:44:27.375 --> 00:44:29.081
You can do it.

00:44:29.106 --> 00:44:31.106
No, I can never do anything.

00:44:31.756 --> 00:44:34.537
- Wait !
- Ying !

00:44:39.159 --> 00:44:42.011
We don’t have a choice anymore. I’m gonna use my power on him.

00:44:42.036 --> 00:44:45.036
Cat Noir ! No !

00:44:45.274 --> 00:44:47.274
Cataclysm !

00:44:49.255 --> 00:44:51.255
No !

00:45:13.418 --> 00:45:13.789
Fei

00:45:14.911 --> 00:45:18.911
Uhhh - Marinette!

00:45:19.698 --> 00:45:21.698
I’m sorry for not forgiving you earlier

00:45:21.994 --> 00:45:29.029
No Marinette! I don’t deserve that you forgive me, I lied to you, I stole your things, and everythings is happening now is my fault

00:45:29.054 --> 00:45:32.657
I can’t imagine the sadness of my father if he saw how I failed

00:45:32.999 --> 00:45:36.040
I know now that you did all of that for a right reason

00:45:36.107 --> 00:45:39.927
Maybe, but i failed to live by my father’s values

00:45:39.990 --> 00:45:43.755
He would never have devoted all his energy to getting revenge on someone

00:45:43.780 --> 00:45:45.942
He would have continued to do good around him

00:45:45.967 --> 00:45:47.967
So, you know what you have to do

00:45:54.068 --> 00:45:56.068
My prodigious!

00:46:08.313 --> 00:46:10.339
Lang!

00:46:17.573 --> 00:46:20.573
Meishi ! Stop destroying everything!

00:46:34.975 --> 00:46:36.809
Tikki, spots on!

00:46:37.808 --> 00:46:39.808
Lucky Charm!

00:46:51.327 --> 00:46:53.327
Perfect!

00:46:57.041 --> 00:46:58.041
Calm down, Meishi!

00:46:58.066 --> 00:47:02.673
I don’t want to hurt you, i’m not here to destroy you neither to satisfy my revenge

00:47:02.698 --> 00:47:05.892
I’m only trying to save you and bring you back to your sense

00:47:06.068 --> 00:47:07.068
I’m no longer Meishi

00:47:07.740 --> 00:47:08.740
I’m Yaloshi

00:47:15.490 --> 00:47:17.490
I went on a shopping spree

00:47:17.613 --> 00:47:20.613
Red and black spots? Funny pattern for a Chinese vase

00:47:21.105 --> 00:47:25.634
It’s because it’s not a chinese vase, but the solution for our problem.

00:47:25.659 --> 00:47:30.971
A giant pill to swallow with plenty of water!
If you see what i’m saying

00:47:31.250 --> 00:47:33.250
I see absolutely, yes

00:47:36.651 --> 00:47:37.651
Yaloshi!

00:47:38.523 --> 00:47:41.265
You came finally to give me what is mine?

00:47:41.290 --> 00:47:43.290
Yes, but before, take a large glass of water to calm you down

00:48:05.132 --> 00:48:06.421
And Voila!

00:48:07.101 --> 00:48:09.210
No more evil doing for you little akuma

00:48:12.999 --> 00:48:14.584
Time to de-evilize

00:48:18.429 --> 00:48:19.289
Gotcha!

00:48:20.351 --> 00:48:22.530
Bye Bye little butterfly

00:48:28.248 --> 00:48:32.726
What happened? You have acceded to the power of the Dragon?

00:48:32.751 --> 00:48:34.751
Yes, with a little bit of help!

00:48:35.443 --> 00:48:36.443
Pound it!

00:48:39.787 --> 00:48:41.827
Was I the one who caused so much damage?

00:48:41.852 --> 00:48:45.016
What a terrible breach of my mission.

00:48:45.041 --> 00:48:50.041
Don’t worry, we’ll take care of fixing everything for you. Miraculous Ladybug!

00:48:58.885 --> 00:48:59.885
Kitty!

00:49:00.807 --> 00:49:04.342
You wrote for the good of all and renounced your revenge.

00:49:04.367 --> 00:49:11.425
You have all the human values required, The Prodigious is in good hand with you, Renren.

00:49:22.912 --> 00:49:27.089
Come on, we forget the past, okay? Just tell me how much do you want?

00:49:27.114 --> 00:49:30.562
Wait! Wait! We can find a solution

00:49:30.587 --> 00:49:35.901
You destroyed my father’s school, you made me an orphan that you forced to steal for you.

00:49:35.926 --> 00:49:39.911
Because of you I renounced all the ancestral values that my father taught me.

00:49:39.936 --> 00:49:44.469
From the beginning you are the source of all the misfortunes that happened to me! Why?

00:49:44.494 --> 00:49:45.354
Money!

00:49:45.405 --> 00:49:51.917
There are no word to describe what you are, but today I decided...

00:49:52.281 --> 00:49:55.198
to let justice take its course.

00:49:55.223 --> 00:49:58.223
Well done, Fei! It’s worthy of a wise "Renren" - full of wisdom

00:50:09.075 --> 00:50:10.341
It’s not too early!

00:50:10.366 --> 00:50:13.034
I was wondering when you were going to decide to put it back on.

00:50:13.059 --> 00:50:14.550
Meishi!

00:50:14.575 --> 00:50:16.591
You thought that my mission was over?

00:50:16.912 --> 00:50:18.494
But it just started

00:50:19.676 --> 00:50:22.771
Ladybug, Cat Noir thank you for your help.

00:50:22.796 --> 00:50:25.015
Well all we have left to do is find Marinette.

00:50:25.040 --> 00:50:28.075
Oh. Yes exactly, we’re here for that after all, finding Marinette!

00:50:28.876 --> 00:50:31.876
Don’t worry, I found her and put her in a shelter during the battle.

00:50:32.021 --> 00:50:37.021
Ying! Are you interested in a little visit to the Shanghai court?

00:50:40.678 --> 00:50:43.075
Uhm, so I suppose that we are going back to Paris together?

00:50:43.100 --> 00:50:45.100
Uhm, yes why not, I mean if you insist.

00:50:46.100 --> 00:50:52.993
Hey, tell me in your opinion, if we want to do a world tour, is it faster to pass by the Arctic or Antarctic?

00:50:53.018 --> 00:50:59.408
Oh what interesting question that I always asked myself but never had the opportunity to answer it, haha.

00:50:59.663 --> 00:51:04.860
You know what? I think that we should test that right now and when we see each other again in Paris we can compare our scores.

00:51:05.476 --> 00:51:08.075
That is an excellent idea Kitty, so i will go that way.

00:51:08.381 --> 00:51:10.751
And I will go that way, until then M’lady.

00:51:19.443 --> 00:51:27.443
You know Marinette, during a birthday, the tradition wants you to inhale the biggest noodle without breaking it. It symbolizes longevity.

00:51:29.075 --> 00:51:34.075
Here in China the 60th birthday is often the first that we celebrate.

00:51:34.222 --> 00:51:35.222
What?! You never celebrated your birthday before?

00:51:37.261 --> 00:51:42.404
Never, and I am really happy to celebrate it for
the first time with you and your boyfriend Adrien.

00:51:42.620 --> 00:51:44.075
Uhm we are only friends.

00:51:45.873 --> 00:51:47.991
Come on it is time for you to open your present.

00:51:52.166 --> 00:51:55.135
Sorry, we didn’t mean to scare you, we only wanted to give you this back.

00:51:56.672 --> 00:51:59.442
Oh, wow my k… my fetish necklace.

00:51:59.467 --> 00:52:01.075
Thank you so much, thank you a thousand times.

00:52:01.713 --> 00:52:03.071
Bring in your friends.

00:52:04.600 --> 00:52:13.059
An accordion? It’s a present from Sabine, Marinette’s mom. I raised her and I always dreamt of playing the accordion

00:52:13.591 --> 00:52:15.075
but I never had the time.

00:52:16.099 --> 00:52:17.465
I know how to play, if you want.

00:52:34.380 --> 00:52:40.625
Congratulations Marinette, you seem to have found the magical ingredient of this meal finally.

00:52:40.650 --> 00:52:46.878
Thank you but i think that if there is a magical ingredient it’s sister Marinette. Does it bother you if I call you sister.

00:52:46.903 --> 00:52:50.441
On the contrary, it’s a pleasure sister Fei. How do we say that in Mandarin?

00:52:50.466 --> 00:52:51.466
Chei Chei.

00:52:51.661 --> 00:52:52.661
Chei Chei Fei.

00:52:54.100 --> 00:52:56.050
What did I say?

00:52:56.075 --> 00:52:59.075
It would be too awkward to translate, Marinette.

00:52:59.100 --> 00:53:02.428
If you want, when we go back to Paris, I could teach you Chinese.

00:53:02.453 --> 00:53:05.100
Otay… I mean yato I mean… ugh.

00:53:06.135 --> 00:53:08.694
Sometimes it’s hard to understand her even in French.

00:53:09.627 --> 00:53:13.968
Coming to China I found more than anything I could have hoped for.

00:53:14.164 --> 00:53:19.476
An incredible uncle, a new friend and a new Chinese teacher.
